<item>
            <title>[DERBY-1772] Error 42Z78 &quot;Failed to locate &apos;Xalan&apos; API  classes&quot; should not have sqlstate class &apos;42&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1772</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a run-time error but it has the SQL state  &apos;42&apos; for compile error, and thus in Java SE 6 will have a SQLException of type SQLSyntaxErrorException.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;ERROR 38000: The exception &apos;java.sql.SQLSyntaxErrorException: Failed to locate &apos;&lt;br/&gt;
Xalan&apos; API or implementation classes.  XML operations are not permitted unless t&lt;br/&gt;
hese classes are in your classpath.&apos; was thrown while evaluating an expression.&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR 42Z78: Failed to locate &apos;Xalan&apos; API or implementation classes.  XML operat&lt;br/&gt;
ions are not permitted unless these classes are in your classpath.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
